explicit goals are sustainibility, restoration and support of functioning ecosystems, true equality of opportunity for all sentient beings, and providing the conditions that will enable sober progress

a recognition of the primacy of Natural interrelationshipas and the sorts of complex self-sustaining dynamic systems that have been present for orders of magnitude more time that humanity has occupied the planet must be kept in mind @ all times

simple strategies involving extractive behavior, wanton destruction, poisoning, polluting and any disregard for so-called "Natural Resources" should be minimized, and ideally, eventually completely eliminated